  m_text: 'This is the dining room. It is filled with people eating at tables. There
    is extensive background dialogue and propoganda inside of it. Many people tell
    you about how the whole ship has been acting up lately.


    You talk to a non-cult
    member, who tells you everyone in here is trapped due to a mysetrious malfuntion
    with the main bridge outside. The engineering team warns people to not leave
    until the problem is fixed. Learning you are an engineer, they open the door
    for you. You then learn to jump and do parkour, as you cross a large pit, and
    reset the power on the other side of the bridge.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
